Package: kanfei
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-venv, adduser, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Self-hosted weather station dashboard and data logger
 Kanfei is a self-hosted weather station dashboard with pluggable hardware
 drivers. It logs sensor data to SQLite and presents it through a modern,
 theme-able browser dashboard with real-time updates and agricultural spray
 advisory.
 .
 Supports Davis Instruments, Ecowitt/Fine Offset, Ambient Weather, and
 WeatherFlow Tempest personal weather stations.
 .
 After installation, browse to http://localhost:8000.
